  }, "Path dependence is the dependence of economic outcomes on the path of previous outcomes, rather than simply on current conditions. In a path-dependent process, \u201Chistory matters\u201D \u2014 it has an enduring influence. Choices made based on transitory conditions can persist long after those conditions change."), mdx("li", {
    parentName: "ol"
